<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
    <head>
        {{> head}}
        <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0, maximum-scale=1.0, user-scalable=no" />
        <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://npmcdn.com/leaflet@1.0.0-rc.1/dist/leaflet.css" />
        <link rel="stylesheet" href="dist/css/style.min.css" media="screen" title="no title" charset="utf-8">

    </head>
    <body>
        {{>header}}
        {{> start}}

        <div id="map">
        </div>
        <div class='ui card' id='hint'>
        <div class='content'>
          <div class='header'>
            小提醒
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="content">
          <div class="ui small feed">
            <div class="event">
              <div class="content">
                <div class="summary">
                  若無任何視窗彈出或是成功定位，請先將瀏覽器設定為
                  <span class='red'>允許彈出視窗</span>以及<span class='red'>同意取得地理資訊</span>
                  ，或是改用 <span class='red'>其他瀏覽器</span>，才可正常瀏覽：）
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="extra content">
          <button class="ui primary button" id='hintButton' >知道了！</button>
        </div>
      </div>
        {{> end}}

        <script src="https://npmcdn.com/leaflet@1.0.0-rc.1/dist/leaflet.js"></script>
        <script type="text/javascript" src='dist/js/index.js'></script>
        {{> footer}}
    </body>
